---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import ContactEmail from '../components/ContactEmail.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Contact the Ramen Guide Editorial Team"
  description="Reach the Ramen Guide editorial team with questions, corrections, story tips, or partnership inquiries about our coverage."
>
  <p>
    The fastest way to reach us is email. We read everything and aim to reply to genuine inquiries
    within a few business days.
  </p>

  <p>
    <ContactEmail class="font-semibold" />
  </p>

  <h2>What to write about</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Corrections:</strong> found an error or a shop that has closed? Tell us and we'll fix it and note the correction.</li>
    <li><strong>Tips &amp; story ideas:</strong> new shops, regional styles, or techniques worth covering.</li>
    <li><strong>Advertising &amp; partnerships:</strong> inquiries about display advertising or sponsorship.</li>
    <li><strong>Privacy requests:</strong> to exercise any of the data rights described in our <a href="/privacy-policy/">privacy policy</a>.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    For how we handle the information you send us, see our
    <a href="/privacy-policy/">privacy policy</a>.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
